CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1966, p. 7B, for obituary of Annie M. Elliot, of 7600 East Lemington Ext., who died June 19, 1966. Her husband was Jesse J. Elliott; her daughters: Elsa Elliott Harris (wife of Charles "Teenie" Harris), Jessie Prince, and sons: Asbury Elliott, Jerry Elliott, Eugene Elliot, and William Elliott of Detroit.
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Annie M. Elliott, wearing dark dress with ruched elbow length sleeves, and necklace of three strands of pearls or beads, posed in front of light colored background, in Harris Studio
